<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Confirmation Email</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f6f9fc;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 40px auto;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
        }

        .header {
            text-align: center;
            padding-bottom: 20px;
        }

            .header h1 {
                color: #333;
            }

        .content {
            font-size: 16px;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #555;
        }

        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            margin-top: 25px;
            padding: 12px 24px;
            background-color: #007bff;
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 6px;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 13px;
            color: #aaa;
            margin-top: 30px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>Welcome to @{Model.ToString();}  </h1>
        </div>
        <div class="content">
       
            <p style="color:cornflowerblue">Thanks for signing up! Your account has been successfully created😊.</p>
            <p>To get started, please confirm your email address by clicking the link inside it..</p>
            <p>If you didn’t create this account, you can safely ignore this email.</p>
            <p>Mhmd Abqader SE🧑‍💻, <br />The IT Team</p>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
            &copy; 2025 [Mhmd Abqader] · <a href="#" style="color:#aaa;">Privacy Policy</a>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
